    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### Understanding Parameters\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Where do 101,770 parameters come from?**\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Flatten → Dense(128)**: 784 × 128 + 128 = 100,480\\n\",\n",
    "    \"  - 784 inputs × 128 neurons = 100,352 weights\\n\",\n",
    "    \"  - 128 biases (one per neuron)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Dense(128) → Dense(10)**: 128 × 10 + 10 = 1,290\\n\",\n",
    "    \"  - 128 inputs × 10 neurons = 1,280 weights\\n\",\n",
    "    \"  - 10 biases\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Total**: 100,480 + 1,290 = **101,770 parameters**\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"These parameters start as random values and get adjusted during training!\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"---\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Part 3: Understanding Model Predictions (Before Training)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Let's see what the untrained model predicts:\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {\n",
    "    \"ExecuteTime\": {\n",
    "     \"end_time\": \"2026-01-13T13:26:54.843421700Z\",\n",
    "     \"start_time\": \"2026-01-13T13:26:54.777149200Z\"\n",
    "    }\n",
    "   },\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Get prediction for first image\\n\",\n",
    "    \"predictions = model(x_train[:1]).numpy()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"Raw output (logits):\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(predictions[0])\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"\\\\nThese are called 'logits' - raw scores for each class.\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"Higher score = more confident prediction\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"# Convert to probabilities using softmax\\n\",\n",
    "    \"probabilities = tf.nn.softmax(predictions[0]).numpy()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"\\\\nProbabilities (after softmax):\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"for digit, prob in enumerate(probabilities):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"  Digit {digit}: {prob:.1%}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"predicted_digit = np.argmax(probabilities)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"\\\\nPredicted digit: {predicted_digit}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"Actual digit: {y_train[0]}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"\\\\n⚠️ Probably wrong! The model hasn't learned anything yet.\\\")\"\n",
    "   ],\n",
